  "body": "<span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #f00;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1054/882/image_2025-01-01_205816908.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"818\" height=\"171\"><br></span></span>\n\n  <br><br><br><br><br>\n\n\n<span style=\"font-size: 24px; color: #0f0;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1054/885/image_2025-01-01_205919969.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"402\" height=\"67\"></span>\n\nCaveBlock is a Minecraft mod that adds blocks to see through walls.\n-------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n  \n\n<span style=\"font-size: 24px; color: #0f0;\"><img src=\"https://korolia.net/images/minecraft/wiki.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"248\" height=\"77\"></span>\n<br><br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">CaveBlock: allows you to see through the walls</span>\n\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">There are a lot of different thypes of cave blocks, you can change thype by using a Stonecutter</span>\n\n<br><br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://korolia.net/images/minecraft/versions.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"402\" height=\"67\"></span>\n\n \n\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">-Forge : 1.18.2 ; 1.19.2 ; 1.19.4 ; 1.20.1</span><br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">-You can see older version [here](https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/caveblock/files)</span>\n<br><br><br><br>\n<span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1054/895/image_2025-01-01_210919031.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"818\" height=\"171\"></span>\n\n\nThis  update adds **20** New Cave Block !!!!",
